<div class="delay-[300ms] duration-[600ms] taos:translate-y-[200px] taos:opacity-0" data-taos-offset="300">
    <div class="duration-[1000ms] [animation-iteration-count:infinite] taos:opacity-0">
        <section class="mt-32 bg-white">
            <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center lg:py-8 lg:px-1">
                <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-black md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">Alumni Memoirs</h1>
                <p class="mb-8 text-4xl font-normal text-black lg:text-xl sm:px-28 xl:px-128">Everybody has a story. And there's something to be learnt from every experience.</p>
                <div class="grid mb-8 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm md:mb-12 md:grid-cols-2 bg-[#f1eedc]" style="box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 10px 36px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06) 0px 0px 0px 1px;">
                    <figure class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 text-center bg-[#f1eedc] border-b border-[#6b502d] rounded-t-lg md:rounded-t-none md:rounded-ss-lg md:border-e">
                        <blockquote class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 text-gray-950 lg:mb-8">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Prioritize continuous upskilling</h3>
                            <p class="my-4">"The technological landscape evolves rapidly, making it crucial for professionals in tech, business, or marketing to stay updated with the latest tools and trends"</p>
                        </blockquote>
                        <figcaption class="flex items-center justify-center">
                            <%- include('../common/imageSkeletonLoader.ejs', {classes:"h-12 w-12 rounded-full" , srcPath:"./media/profileImages/memoir_rishabh.jpeg", altPath:""}) %>
                            <div class="space-y-0.5 font-medium text-left rtl:text-right ms-3">
                                <div>Rishabh Shukla</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-950">Product Manager at Paytm</div>
                            </div>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    <figure class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 text-center bg-[#f1eedc] border-b border-[#6b502d] md:rounded-se-lg">
                        <blockquote class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 text-gray-950 lg:mb-8">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Don't try to get too far ahead of yourself</h3>
                            <p class="my-4">"If you consider the process as an investment towards the end goal, then you're creating far worse opportunity cost for yourself. So, for all the selfish reasons, start enjoying the process."</p>
                        </blockquote>
                        <figcaption class="flex items-center justify-center">
                            <%- include('../common/imageSkeletonLoader.ejs', {classes:"h-12 w-12 rounded-full" , srcPath:"./media/profileImages/memoir_prabhas.jpeg", altPath:""}) %>
                            <div class="space-y-0.5 font-medium text-left rtl:text-right ms-3">
                                <div>Prabhash Jain</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-950">Associate Software Engineer, Microsoft</div>
                            </div>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    <figure class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 text-center bg-[#f1eedc] border-b border-[#6b502d] md:rounded-es-lg md:border-b-0 md:border-e">
                        <blockquote class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 text-gray-950 lg:mb-8">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Benefit from the experiences of your seniors</h3>
                            <p class="my-4">"Without doing something wrong, you will never know that you are doing anything wrong, and without talking, you will never realize that you are. So talk to your seniors, reach out to your alumni, learn to benefit from their experiences."</p>
                        </blockquote>
                        <figcaption class="flex items-center justify-center">
                            <%- include('../common/imageSkeletonLoader.ejs', {classes:"h-12 w-12 rounded-full" , srcPath:"./media/profileImages/memoir_ujjwal.jpeg", altPath:""}) %>
                            <div class="space-y-0.5 font-medium text-left rtl:text-right ms-3">
                                <div>Ujjwal Anand</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-950">Senior Software Engineer, Razorpay</div>
                            </div>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    <figure class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 text-center bg-[#f1eedc] border-[#6b502d] rounded-b-lg md:rounded-se-lg">
                        <blockquote class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 text-gray-950 lg:mb-8">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Avoid Deadline pressure</h3>
                            <p class="my-4">"My aversion to deadline pressure, the prospect of a chill life coupled with continuous learning fueled my passion for research, shaped my career trajectory."</p>
                        </blockquote>
                        <figcaption class="flex items-center justify-center">
                            <%- include('../common/imageSkeletonLoader.ejs', {classes:"h-12 w-12 rounded-full" , srcPath:"./media/profileImages/memoir_krati.jpeg", altPath:""}) %>
                            <div class="space-y-0.5 font-medium text-left rtl:text-right ms-3">
                                <div>Krati Saxena</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-950">Senior Software Engineer, Alien Technology Transfer</div>
                            </div>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
